lead_paragraph: Australia coach Ange Postecoglou has recalled forwards Tommy Oar and Nathan Burns in an extended 30-man squad for next month's World Cup qualifier against Thailand after being disappointed with the Socceroos' disjointed attack in the home draw against Japan.

headline.print_headline: Postecoglou Recalls Burns, Oar in Extended Australia Squad
